Netflix is flexible. There are no pesky contracts and no commitments. You can easily cancel your account online in two clicks. There are no cancellation fees — start or stop your account at any time.
How does the free trial work?

Try us free for 30 days! If you enjoy your Netflix trial, do nothing and your membership will automatically continue for as long as you choose to remain a member. Cancel at any time before your trial ends and you won’t be charged. There’s no complicated contract, no cancellation fees and no commitment. Cancel online at any time, 24 hours a day.
What’s different on an ad-supported plan?

An ad-supported plan is a great way to enjoy movies and TV shows at a lower price. You can stream your favourites with limited ad breaks (some location and device restrictions apply). Downloads are not supported and a limited number of movies and TV shows are not available due to licensing restrictions. Learn more.
